{"tid":1844032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 暴徒於粉嶺進行破壞及縱火","createTime":"2020-01-26T12:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T13:48:17.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"27e49b72a63f82f91c714574a3b59ec434ba580d","tid":1844032,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"暴徒於粉嶺進行破壞及縱火<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n<br />\n  今日（一月二十六日）由下午四時開始，有暴徒於粉嶺暉明邨路口以雜物及磚頭堵路，影響現場交通，警方曾派員到場清理路障，但暴徒仍然罔顧法紀。<br />\n<br />\n  至傍晚時份，暴徒破壞暉明路和華明路交界的交通燈，及以汽油彈於大廈大堂內縱火，危害現場人士的人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n  警方警告暴徒立即停止違法行為及將會採取執法行動。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年1月26日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間20時22分"},{"pid":"852f319b588cfa015f8ed75b813b86e096c65277","tid":1844032,"uid":1099,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:40:17.000Z","msg":"佢地只係一班保家衛族嘅居民<br />\n又睇唔到佢地手持武器<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798d3e631120fd14e1a5b7a70c1ba398c7d9b133","tid":1844032,"uid":58209,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"藍屍:!?"},{"pid":"26bfa656bffe42e1f1397437ed70ce2888cb7a29","tid":1844032,"uid":28068,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"證明今次行動做得非常之好<br />\n要繼續進攻機場同羅湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2524493fd98d310b73b621ace9571b6240e5648a","tid":1844032,"uid":78039,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"無論你係藍定黃，做政府唔鐘意既野就係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889c19bee45e2786dbf28fbaf30ce10180ea5016","tid":1844032,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face